sql_query.sql: SELECT "invites".* FROM "invites" WHERE ("invites"."deleted_at" IS NULL) AND "invites"."invite_key" = 'cab19cf667ee822ce1d4acbb235de3ea' LIMIT 1
UPDATE "invites" SET redeemed_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP WHERE ("invites"."deleted_at" IS NULL) AND (id = 28 AND redeemed_at IS NULL AND updated_at >= '2020-04-28 19:04:22.439973')
DELETE FROM "invites" WHERE ("invites"."deleted_at" IS NULL) AND (invites.email = 'iceking@adventuretime.ooo' AND redeemed_at IS NULL AND invites.id != 28)
